      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "FUGAKU (7) impressed in her last trial and looks set to fire on debut for Team Williams and Lucy Fiore. She should be well positioned from the barrier draw and Fiore did partner her in her first trial back in February. Can make a statement on debut. FREE RIDE (1) tackled two Saturday races to begin his campaign and wasn't disgraced in those stronger events. He'll be fitter for a recent trial where he was solid and the inside draw today is a big help. CJP rides and he can notch up his maiden win. BLUE TANG (6) bolted in at the trials recently and looks set for a bold showing on debut. She's a half to the handy Tonkin and it wouldn't surprise to see her fire. VIOLET VICTORY (5) improved with the blinkers on in his latest trial and with an inside draw today, he won't be far away. TWICE THE RAIN (2) can improve with the debut effort under his belt.",
